Do some warm up and stretch excersies or a brisk walk. It will help prevent injures. You can try 5-10 reps of: leg swings (forwards & sideways), lunges (front, back & lateral), arms swings, trunk rotations etc.
Don't feel pressured to continue faster than you're able.
Take your time to recover during walking
You can do 3-5 minutes of brisk then gentle walking, then leg and total body stretches
